=============================================================================
EXAMPLE RENDERINGS
=============================================================================

These examples show what each macro produces.

{{ ironic_generalization("It is a truth universally acknowledged", "by Nobody") }}
→ "It is a truth universally acknowledged — by Nobody —"

{{ free_indirect_dash("She observed his Countenance", "it told her nothing she wished to know") }}
→ "She observed his Countenance — it told her nothing she wished to know —"

{{ tell_it_slant("She did not look at him", "which told him everything") }}
→ "She did not look at him — which told him everything —"

{{ stanza_paragraph(
    "The Dinner Party assembled with all the Civility that Society requires",
    "and none of the Warmth that Nature demands",
    "The Soup was cold",
    "which is to say — Honest"
) }}
→
The Dinner Party assembled with all the Civility that Society requires.
and none of the Warmth that Nature demands —
The Soup was cold.
which is to say — Honest —

{{ nobody_declaration("She") }}
→ "She was Nobody — which is to say — Free —"

{{ soul_door("Miss Bennet", "her own Understanding") }}
→ "Miss Bennet selected her own Understanding — then shut the Door —"

{{ hymnal_paragraph(
    "She had lived twenty years in the neighbourhood with very little to vex her",
    "which was its own kind of Eternity"
) }}
→
She had lived twenty years in the neighbourhood with very little to vex her.
which was its own kind of Eternity —

{{ emily_austin_letter_opening("Friend") }}
→ "Dear Friend —"

{{ emily_austin_letter_close("E") }}
→ "Yours — E —"

{{ circumference("tea-table") }}
→ "— the tea-table was Circumference —"

{{ epigrammatic_opening("A Woman of seven and twenty is a Problem — or a Portent —") }}
→ "A Woman of seven and twenty is a Problem — or a Portent —"

{{ devastating_close("She smiled — and was Nobody — which is to say — Free —") }}
→ "She smiled — and was Nobody — which is to say — Free —"

=============================================================================
#}
